# Authentication & Security

## Setup
- NextAuth.js (Auth.js) v5, App Router compatible
- Session: database-backed (PrismaAdapter) atau JWT
- **Credentials**: email + password; hash dengan bcrypt/argon2 — dilarang plaintext
- **OAuth**: Google & Facebook; link akun lokal jika email sama

## Roles
- `CUSTOMER` (default) dan `ADMIN`

### Page Protection
- `/account/*`, `/checkout/*`: wajib login → redirect `/auth/login`
- `/admin/*`: login + role `ADMIN`; non-admin → 403 atau redirect `/` dengan peringatan
- `/auth/login`, `/auth/register`: user sudah login → redirect `/` (customer) atau `/admin` (admin)

### API Protection
Routes `/api/user/*`, `/api/cart/*`, `/api/orders/*`, `/api/admin/*`:
- Gunakan `auth()` dari NextAuth
- Session null → `401` + `{ "error": "Unauthorized" }`
- `/api/admin/*` tanpa role `ADMIN` → `403` + `{ "error": "Forbidden" }`

## Input Validation
- Semua payload API divalidasi dengan Zod sebelum ke database
- Email: `.toLowerCase()` + `.trim()`
- Validasi gagal → `400 Bad Request` + detail error

## Environment
- `NEXTAUTH_SECRET`: entropy tinggi, min 32 karakter, di `.env.local`
- Production: cookie `secure: true`
- CSRF: gunakan proteksi bawaan NextAuth untuk POST/PATCH/DELETE
